(6, 'Indraprastha College For Women', NULL, 'Indraprastha College For Women in New Delhi, Delhi Admission 2026 Fees Courses Placement', 'Indraprastha College For Women', 'which comprises of events like - Inter College Cross-Country Run and Athletic Meet for PwD students also, The Indraprastha Invitational Badminton & Tennis Tournament which witnesses participation from students of different colleges of the University of Delhi is regularly held.', 'Overview:\nIndraprastha College For Women IP IGNOU Center About Us About Us Code of Professional Ethics Media Coverage Governing Body Academics Departments Centers Research Cell Academic Collaborations IQAC IQAC AQAR NIRF Facilities College Support Services Academic Infrastructure ICT Resources Student Life Student Residences Societies Committees Anti Ragging Committee NEP 2020 Internal Complaint Committee Career Counselling and Placement Committee Anti Drug Committee Grievance Redressal Committee Mental Health Committee Cells UBA Cell Anti Smoking Cell Equal Opportunity Cell & Anti-Discriminatory Officer EWS Cell Minority Cell OBC Cell SC/ST Cell Student Counsellor Student Grievances Student Testimonials Curriculum Description NEP Framework Syllabus Notifications College Academic Calendar IP Radio Administration Organogram Administration Staff Non Teaching Staff Technical Staff Contractual Employees Finances Financial Reports Financial Aid Examination Time Table Sports SHE-Box Viksit Bharat@2047 Óż░ÓżŠÓż£ÓżŁÓżŠÓżĘÓżŠ ÓżĖÓż«Óż┐ÓżżÓż┐ Azadi Ka Amrit Mahotsav Staff Seniority List Staff Council Committees Recruitment NPU Alumni Prof. Poonam Kumria Principal\'s message It is with immense pride and gratitude that I welcome you to Indraprastha College for Women ŌĆö the oldest and first women\'s college of the University of Delhi, with a proud legacy spanning over a century. Established in May 1924, the College has been a pioneer in women\'s education in India, nurturing generations of empowered, confident, and socially responsible women. Rooted in the ideals of excellence, equity, and service, the College continues to uphold its rich heritage while embracing the opportunities of the future. Announcement General Students Staff Accreditation IQAC AQAR NIRF Admission UG Admissions PG Admissions Hostel Admissions Stude.\n\nContact Details:\nilm Festival IP Stories Jan 01, 2023 Fact Checking Workshop Useful Links Samanavay 2026 100 Years of Celebrations RTI Ordinances Roster Tenders & Quotations Downloads College Library Museum & Archives Student Residences Contact Us Copyright ┬® 2026. All rights reserved | Powered by Mobiquel ├Ś Indraprastha College For Women IP IGNOU Center About Us About Us Code of Professional Ethics Media Coverage Governing Body Academics Departments Centers R\nostel Admission Hostel Admission S.No. Title Link 1 Information bulletin of Student Residences View View Archived RTI Ordinances Roster Tenders & Quotations Downloads College Library Museum & Archives Student Residences Contact Us Copyright ┬® 2026. All rights reserved | Powered by Mobiquel ├Ś Indraprastha College For Women IP IGNOU Center About Us About Us Code of Professional Ethics Media Coverage Governing Body Academics Departments Centers R\nonducting virtual sports fitness classes for the students and various events for the college staff and community. RTI Ordinances Roster Tenders & Quotations Downloads College Library Museum & Archives Student Residences Contact Us Copyright ┬® 2026. All rights reserved | Powered by Mobiquel ├Ś Indraprastha College For Women IP IGNOU Center About Us About Us Code of Professional Ethics Media Coverage Governing Body Academics Departments Centers R\nbasis of Sports Supernumerary Quota in Undergraduate Programs 2025-2026 View 2 ECA Undertaking View View Archived RTI Ordinances Roster Tenders & Quotations Downloads College Library Museum & Archives Student Residences Contact Us Copyright ┬® 2026. All rights reserved | Powered by Mobiquel ├Ś Indraprastha College For Women IP IGN